PN,40601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FThe mother of a five-year-old boy
OL,7,Fabducted by his British father, who
OL,8,Fwas wrongly released from prison and
OL,9,Fis believed to have since left the UK,
OL,10,Ffeels "betrayed" by prison authorities
OL,11,Fand says the blunder has meant she has
OL,12,F"lost all hope".
OL,14,FClaire N'Djosse has not seen her son,
OL,15,FLaurys N'Djosse Adeyeye, for almost
OL,16,Ftwo years after he was abducted in
OL,17,FFrance by Ifedayo Adeyeye in July
OL,18,F2024, with Laurys taken to Nigeria via
OL,19,Fthe UK.
OL,26,@rD@GOUrD@PO]tD@AOUtD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FShe has since sought to have Laurys
OL,7,Freturned to her care through the High
OL,8,FCourt in London, with Adeyeye
OL,9,Fsentenced to 18 months in prison for
OL,10,Fcontempt of court after failing to
OL,11,Freturn Laurys to her.
OL,13,FBut the court heard earlier this month
OL,14,Fthat Adeyeye, a 58-year-old dual
OL,15,FBritish-Nigerian national, was wrongly
OL,16,Freleased from HMP Pentonville in
OL,17,FLondon on April 21 and may have
OL,18,Ftravelled to Spain in the three days
OL,19,Fit took prison staff to notify police.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FPolice are continuing to search for
OL,7,FAdeyeye, with the Ministry of Justice
OL,8,F(MoJ) saying that it understood the
OL,9,Fdistress the mistaken release had
OL,10,Fcaused.
OL,12,FSpeaking in French and translated by a
OL,13,FPress Association reporter, Ms
OL,14,FN'Djosse said she was "lost" without
OL,15,Fher son and that her "life stopped"
OL,16,Fwhen Laurys was abducted, leaving her
OL,17,Ffeeling that she was "going to die".
OL,26,@vD@WOUvD@\O]wD@VOUwD@cO]yD@VOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FThe 46-year-old continued that
OL,7,FAdeyeye's imprisonment had given her a
OL,8,F"glimmer of hope" that Laurys would be
OL,9,Freturned, but that his release meant
OL,10,F"my life stopped again".
OL,12,FShe said: "It's my child who's my
OL,13,Fhope. My life has stopped; I can't do
OL,14,Fanything if I don't have my child. My
OL,15,Fchild is my reason to live."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@QO]rD@AOUrD@WO]tD@KOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FShe continued: "Although it was
OL,7,Fdifficult, I told myself, 'I'm going
OL,8,Fto live in hope. Now that (Adeyeye) is
OL,9,Fin the justice system's hands,
OL,10,Fwhatever happens, I will have my
OL,11,Fchild'. I tried to have the strength."
OL,13,FShe continued: "Now that Adeyeye is
OL,14,Fgone again, I have lost all hope of
OL,15,Fseeing my child again. I am upset. I
OL,16,Fdon't know how I'm going to keep
OL,17,Fgoing."
OL,26,@nD@POUsD@fO]uD@POUyD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FReferring to Pentonville prison, Ms
OL,7,FN'Djosse said she "felt betrayed where
OL,8,FI believed him to be the most secure"
OL,9,Fand called for an investigation into
OL,10,FAdeyeye's release, adding she wanted
OL,11,F"justice for this injustice".
OL,13,FShe said: "The UK Government must see
OL,14,Fthat it is not OK. I am a victim, I am
OL,15,Funfortunately a victim, and it's very
OL,16,Fserious."
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@eO]sD@AOUsD@\O]uD@KOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FIn a ruling last June, Mr Justice
OL,7,FHayden said Laurys was born in France
OL,8,Fand had lived with his mother since
OL,9,Fbirth, but was abducted on July 27
OL,10,F2024 during his first overnight stay
OL,11,Fwith his father.
OL,13,FA Nigerian court later gave parental
OL,14,Fresponsibility for him to two people,
OL,15,Fbelieved to be Adeyeye's relatives,
OL,16,Fwithout Ms N'Djosse's consent.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FIn a legal first, Mr Justice Hayden
OL,7,Fruled that the High Court had the
OL,8,Fpower to order that Adeyeye return
OL,9,FLaurys to his mother, even though the
OL,10,Fboy did not live in the UK.
OL,12,FThe judge said the abduction was "an
OL,13,Fact of cruelty that even this court
OL,14,Frarely sees" and described Adeyeye as
OL,15,Fa "dangerous threat to his son's
OL,16,Fphysical and emotional welfare".
OL,26,@tD@bOUvD@LO]wD@COUxD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FAdeyeye was arrested upon returning to
OL,7,Fthe UK and, in January, was first
OL,8,Fsentenced to six months in prison for
OL,9,Fcontempt of court after failing to
OL,10,Freturn Laurys.
OL,12,FHe was sentenced to a further 12
OL,13,Fmonths on April 20 but was wrongly
OL,14,Freleased the following day, despite
OL,15,Falso being due to be extradited to
OL,16,FFrance upon completion of his sentence.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FA hearing on May 11 was told that
OL,7,FAdeyeye is believed to have travelled
OL,8,Fto Spain on April 22, but prison staff
OL,9,Fdid not tell police about his release
OL,10,Funtil April 24.
OL,12,FMr Justice Hayden said the public was
OL,13,F"entitled to expect far better" and
OL,14,Fthat the state had "failed", adding
OL,15,Fthere was an "alarming lack of
OL,16,Furgency" from prison staff.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@_O]vD@TOUvD@[O]wD@NOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FMs N'Djosse, who lives in south-east
OL,7,FFrance, said she did not criticise the
OL,8,FEnglish courts and that she had been
OL,9,F"on the right path to get my child
OL,10,Fback", but that this was "wrecked" by
OL,11,FAdeyeye's release.
OL,13,FShe continued that Laurys was being
OL,14,F"manipulated like a puppet" and urged
OL,15,Fanyone with information related to
OL,16,FAdeyeye's whereabouts, including his
OL,17,Ffamily, to come forward.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@EO]rD@ZOUrD@bO]vD@AOUvD@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FShe said: "My child wants to come back
OL,7,Fto see his mum. My child does not
OL,8,Fdeserve all this. Why is my child
OL,9,Fbeing punished?"
OL,11,FShe continued: "I am a lost mum.
OL,12,FWithout my child, I don't have a life.
OL,13,FI want to find my child.
OL,15,F"I beg you to hear my screams, I beg
OL,16,Fyou, those who are already parents,
OL,17,Fthose who aren't parents yet, I beg
OL,18,Fyou."
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@PO]sD@POUwD@AOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FData published by the MoJ last month
OL,7,Fshowed that 179 inmates were wrongly
OL,8,Freleased between April 2025 and March
OL,9,F2026.
OL,11,FIt is understood that a review into
OL,12,FAdeyeye's release is ongoing, with a
OL,13,Fspokesperson for the department
OL,14,Fstating that it had accepted 33
OL,15,Frecommendations from an independent
OL,16,Freview into accidental releases across
OL,17,Fthe prison system.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,FThey said: "We completely understand
OL,7,Fthe distress that this release in
OL,8,Ferror has caused to Claire N'Djosse,
OL,9,Fand our thoughts remain with her and
OL,10,Fher family.
OL,12,F"We are urgently working with the
OL,13,Fpolice to recapture this individual.
OL,15,F"The Government inherited a prison
OL,16,Fsystem in crisis after years of
OL,17,Funderinvestment, which has resulted in
OL,18,Funacceptable rises in release in
OL,19,Ferrors.
OL,26,@nD@LOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780323077
OL,3,CMother outraged after son's abductor
OL,4,Caccidentally released from prison
OL,6,F"That's why we're investing up to #82
OL,7,Fmillion to digitise outdated paper-
OL,8,Fbased systems, roll out biometrics and
OL,9,Fstrengthen checks so we can better
OL,10,Fprotect the public."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/15
